<font color="#ffa500">Isn't that the way?</font>

404
00:21:09,040 --> 00:21:17,010
<font color="#ffa500">Everybody's got their dues in life to pay...</font>

405
00:21:17,540 --> 00:21:20,020
<font color="#ffa500">Yeah I know</font>

406
