<font color="#ffa500">In books' written pages</font>

412
00:21:44,070 --> 00:21:46,200
<font color="#ffa500">Lived and learned</font>

413
00:21:46,200 --> 00:21:51,200
<font color="#ffa500">From fools and from sages</font>

414
00:21:51,710 --> 00:21:56,020
<font color="#ffa500">You know it's true</font>

415
00:21:56,700 --> 00:21:59,520
<font color="#ffa500">All the things</font>

416
00:21:59,520 --> 00:22:02,550
<font color="#ffa500">Come back to you</font>

