659
00:35:05,790 --> 00:35:10,190
没有标签 没有先入之见
只有他们真正的心灵

660
00:35:11,070 --> 00:35:15,360
是的 他们大多数人都不是明星...

661
00:35:16,390 --> 00:35:18,820
但他们同明星一样闪耀

662
00:35:19,110 --> 00:35:21,680
你知道恒星死亡后会怎么样吗?

663
00:35:21,680 --> 00:35:22,830
它不会消失

664
00:35:22,830 --> 00:35:26,630
它会变成黑洞 巨大的吸引能量的物质

665
00:35:26,630 --> 00:35:28,820
并不仅仅是自我塌缩

666
00:35:28,820 --> 00:35:31,720
它还会吸走任何靠近的光线

667
00:35:31,720 --> 00:35:37,300
你夺走合唱团 就不只是
熄灭了孩子们的光芒

668
00:35:37,620 --> 00:35:41,660
你又创造了13个黑洞

669
00:35:46,890 --> 00:35:50,030
我想让你接替我的角色

670
00:35:50,940 --> 00:35:54,390
你才应该扮演冉阿让

671
00:35:59,090 --> 00:36:03,560
我希望你知道
艺术对一个人的心灵有多么重要

672
00:36:03,560 --> 00:36:06,100
你已经是个黑洞了

673
00:36:06,410 --> 00:36:10,130
或许这能让你想起曾是明星的时候

674
00:36:10,130 --> 00:36:12,860
那就是说

675
00:36:12,860 --> 00:36:17,740
如果我不取消项目 你就把角色让给我

676
00:36:17,740 --> 00:36:18,800
正是

677
00:36:18,800 --> 00:36:20,900
好 成交

678
00:36:20,900 --> 00:36:22,020
先生 你好

679
00:36:22,020 --> 00:36:25,400
我是你的新主演
我想马上定一些基本的规矩

680
00:36:25,400 --> 00:36:28,520
首先 我有一大堆点子 然后...

681
00:36:28,520 --> 00:36:31,040
我并不会听指挥

682
00:36:33,850 --> 00:36:35,510
Jessie 你在这儿干什么?

683
00:36:35,510 --> 00:36:37,810
我说过要帮你梦想成真

684
00:36:37,810 --> 00:36:39,010
不 我还没准备好

685
00:36:39,010 --> 00:36:41,940
不 你准备好了

686
00:36:53,230 --> 00:36:56,800
嗨 宝贝 我是你的母亲

687
00:36:56,800 --> 00:37:00,090
我想一切尽在歌声中

688
00:37:01,010 --> 00:37:08,410
<font color=#f00000>I dreamed a dream in time gone by</font>

689
00:37:08,410 --> 00:37:10,130
<font color=#f00000>When hope was high</font>

690
00:37:10,130 --> 00:37:14,980
<font color=#f00000>And life worth living</font>

691
00:37:15,580 --> 00:37:22,520
<font color=#f00000>I dreamed that love would never die</font>

692
00:37:22,520 --> 00:37:30,400
<font color=#f00000>I dreamed that God would be forgiving</font>

693
00:37:30,400 --> 00:37:37,430
<font color=#f00000>Then I was young and unafraid </font>

694
00:37:37,430 --> 00:37:39,100
<font color=#f00000>And dreams were made</font>

695
00:37:39,100 --> 00:37:44,470
<font color=#f00000>And used and wasted</font>

696
00:37:44,470 --> 00:37:51,610
<font color=#f00000>There was no ransom to be paid</font>

697
00:37:51,610 --> 00:37:59,140
<font color=#f00000>No song unsung no wine untasted</font>

698
00:37:59,330 --> 00:38:06,030
<font color=#f00000>But the tigers come at night</font>

699
00:38:06,030 --> 00:38:12,830
<font color=#f00000>With their voices soft as thunder</font>

700
00:38:12,830 --> 00:38:19,680
<font color=#f00000>As they tear your hope apart</font>

701
00:38:19,680 --> 00:38:33,160
<font color=#f00000>As they turn your dream to shame..</font>

702
00:38:33,880 --> 00:38:40,080
<font color=#f00000>And still I dream she'll come to me</font>

703
00:38:40,080 --> 00:38:46,470
<font color=#f00000>That we will live the years together </font>

704
00:38:46,470 --> 00:38:52,940
<font color=#f00000>But there are dreams that cannot be</font>

705
00:38:52,940 --> 00:39:00,280
<font color=#f00000>And there are storms we cannot weather</font>

706
00:39:02,950 --> 00:39:04,690
<font color=#f00000>I had a dream</font>

707
00:39:04,690 --> 00:39:09,360
<font color=#f00000>My life would be</font>

708
00:39:09,360 --> 00:39:13,570
<font color=#f00000>So different from this hell I'm living</font>

709
00:39:13,570 --> 00:39:14,900
<font color=#f00000>So different now</font>

710
00:39:14,900 --> 00:39:19,930
<font color=#f00000>From what it seemed</font>

711
00:39:21,390 --> 00:39:27,600
<font color=#f00000>Now life has killed the dream</font>

712
00:39:28,520 --> 00:39:37,350
<font color=#f00000>I dreamed</font>

713
00:39:49,260 --> 00:39:51,190
Artie 拜托 再考虑下

714
00:39:51,190 --> 00:39:53,110
考虑过了

715
00:39:53,110 --> 00:39:56,700
你为这段舞付出了这么多
不该只有个残疾搭档

716
00:39:56,700 --> 00:40:01,690
事实上 团里任何一个男生
不排练都能比我跳得好

717
00:40:01,690 --> 00:40:03,030
除了Finn

718
00:40:03,030 --> 00:40:04,630
但我想和你跳

719
00:40:04,630 --> 00:40:08,920
我跳不了舞 永远也不能

720
00:40:08,920 --> 00:40:11,280
但...没关系

721
00:40:11,280 --> 00:40:15,550
反正我也不可能灌篮或者猎杀狮子

722
00:40:15,550 --> 00:40:19,580
我要专注于能够实现的梦想

723
00:40:19,950 --> 00:40:23,380
我很好 Tina 真的

724
00:40:29,900 --> 00:40:32,640
你至少能唱这首歌吧?

725
00:40:32,640 --> 00:40:34,880
当然

726
00:40:40,450 --> 00:40:42,470
各位 听着

727
00:40:42,470 --> 00:40:44,840
Tina有节目与大家分享 但首先

728
00:40:44,840 --> 00:40:47,110
我要做个声明

729
00:40:47,300 --> 00:40:49,550
你们都获得缓刑了

730
00:40:49,550 --> 00:40:52,200
Bryan Ryan不会砍掉合唱团

731
00:40:54,780 --> 00:40:55,730
他死了吗?

732
00:40:55,730 --> 00:40:57,690
不 他没死

733
00:40:57,690 --> 00:41:02,490
他这几个月会忙于主演"悲惨世界"

734
00:41:02,490 --> 00:41:03,800
他拿到了主角

735
00:41:03,800 --> 00:41:05,380
我以为你是主角

736
00:41:05,380 --> 00:41:07,030
我退出了

737
00:41:07,030 --> 00:41:09,170
这是保留合唱团的代价

738
00:41:09,170 --> 00:41:10,680
很遗憾让你这样 Shue老师

739
00:41:10,680 --> 00:41:12,390
不遗憾

740
00:41:12,390 --> 00:41:14,810
在我看来

741
00:41:14,810 --> 00:41:20,350
我以我一个人的梦想
换来了你们13个人实现梦想的机会

742
00:41:20,350 --> 00:41:23,090
这可不是个小数目

743
00:41:23,090 --> 00:41:25,290
先从Tina的梦开始吧

744
00:41:25,290 --> 00:41:27,210
来吧 Tina

745
00:41:28,650 --> 00:41:31,290
我知道你为我们打造了一段舞蹈

746
00:41:31,290 --> 00:41:34,690
一段可能在地区赛上使用的大作

747
00:41:34,690 --> 00:41:37,790
有舞伴吗?

748
00:41:38,370 --> 00:41:40,550
Mike Chang

749
00:41:49,080 --> 00:41:54,630
<font color=#0cc2d0>Stars shining bright above you</font>

750
00:41:54,630 --> 00:42:00,020
<font color=#0cc2d0>Night breezes seem to whisper
"I love you"</font>

751
00:42:00,020 --> 00:42:04,790
<font color=#0cc2d0>Birds singing in the sycamore tree</font>

752
00:42:04,790 --> 00:42:09,740
<font color=#0cc2d0>Dream a little dream of me</font>

753
00:42:10,890 --> 00:42:16,010
<font color=#0cc2d0>Say nightynight and kiss me</font>

754
00:42:16,350 --> 00:42:21,660
<font color=#0cc2d0>Just hold me tight
and tell me you'll miss me</font>

755
00:42:21,660 --> 00:42:26,680
<font color=#0cc2d0>While I'm alone and blue as can be</font>

756
00:42:26,680 --> 00:42:31,000
<font color=#0cc2d0>Dream a little dream of me</font>

757
00:42:54,490 --> 00:42:59,290
<font color=#0cc2d0>Sweet dreams till sunbeams find you</font>

758
00:42:59,290 --> 00:43:05,880
<font color=#0cc2d0>Sweet dreams that leave all worries
far behind you</font>

759
00:43:05,880 --> 00:43:10,270
<font color=#0cc2d0>But in your dreams whatever they be</font>

760
00:43:10,270 --> 00:43:19,660
<font color=#0cc2d0>Dream a little dream of me
dream a little dream of me</font>

761
00:43:20,061 --> 00:43:21,060
<font color=38B0DE>欢乐合唱团 第一季第19集
完</font>


